## Conversation list item content

Each item should support:

* avatar
* display name
* last message preview
* unread badge
* time label
* active state
* muted/pinned indicators if applicable

## UX rules

* list should be quickly scannable
* active state should be obvious
* unread should be visually clear
* hover should be subtle
* long names and previews should truncate gracefully

