## Message list behavior

The message list must support:

* grouped messages by sender/time proximity
* date separators
* scrollable content area
* loading older messages if needed
* empty state
* typing indicator
* stable composer positioning

## Message bubble rules

Messages should clearly distinguish:

* own message
* other user message
* group sender context if needed
* time/status
* attachments

## Composer rules

The composer must support:

* text input
* multiline growth
* send action
* attachment trigger
* disabled/loading states
* keyboard-friendly usage

